text: haey yeung minban banhchoun anakneasar mk krawpi thveuchea anak phdal damnoeng rikreay ning chea anak dasatuen promean( dl mnoussa lok) noh laey . te puok del ban brachheang chchek denhdaol knea nung brakear min troemotrauv daembi bambat nouv brakear troemotrauv daoy puokke ban yk banda phosdo tang robsa yeung ning avei del trauv ban promean puokke noh mk lengsaech chamakalakleuy towvinh
